rows.label: tlk70000043_05_msg0001
rows.name:
I'm so glad to have had such valuable
experiences. My thanks to you for your
help!

rows.label: tlk70000043_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Kozel-san and Shin both blew me away
with their cooking. My expectations
were far too low

rows.label: tlk70000043_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm not trying to butter you up or
anything, but it was a great contest.
What an honor to be a judge!

rows.label: tlk70000043_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Mmm! Ah, and Hikari's cooking
was something special too!

rows.label: tlk70000043_05_msg0005
rows.name:
That kind of addictive cooking is
more like some kind of poison!

rows.label: tlk70000043_05_msg0006
rows.name:
It'll keep my regular customers
happy, tha's for sure.

rows.label: tlk70000043_05_msg0007
rows.name:
Huh? Er, no, I don't mean to sound like
I wish my regulars any harm... Just
trust me. Superbians'll love it.
